的乌克兰痕迹，是因为可能破坏德乌关系…全是类似的路数，此乃幼儿痴语」。（参考消息）拉夫罗夫：若「北溪」被炸调查遭阻止，俄会考虑报复西方"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-cdf51a6eb35c21cdbb2a1e287b8dc7ec_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/589082676"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIuPKP9ZzNq59REAMaCDkzMTg4OTMzIOvBtaAGMAg4gAFAJXIJNTg5MDgyNjc2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1678684106.2487574", "card_id": "Q_587925815", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 88}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "平淡饮食，规律锻炼，会拥有一个好身体吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "现在的人越来越养生了，每天规律锻炼，清淡饮食，规律作息。这样做真的会拥有一个好身体，不生病吗？ @知乎运动 @知乎健康"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/587925815"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IuPKP9ZzNq59REAMaCDkyOTMxODY0IM6bl6AGMAA4akAmcgk1ODc5MjU4MTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1678684106.249494", "card_id": "Q_588254276", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 16}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么各大文明早期的整块胸甲都在之后走向没落？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-88d746ffea5d78cc55b36b23efb604a2_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/588254276"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIuPKP9ZzNq59REAMaCDkzMDA1MDA0IK2IoKAGMAA4KkAncgk1ODgyNTQyNzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1",